The third version of this MIB module. Contact info updated and Revision history added.

nortelNMIconfigNotiMIB.contactinfo: Jingdong Liu Postal: Nortel Networks P. O. Box 3511, Station C Ottawa, Ontario CANADA K1Y 4H7 Email: jingdong@nortelnetworks.com
nortelNMIconfigNotiMIB.description: This module contains the configuration management related notifications for the Nortel NMI.

nortelNMIconfigNotiPrefix.name: nortelNMIconfigNotiPrefix
nortelNMIconfigNotiPrefix.description: This OID represents the prefix branch for all Nortel NMI configuration Notifications. The last but one sub identifier in the OID of any Notification must have the value zero to facilitate v2<-->v1 conversion.

nortelNMIconfigNotiVarbinds.name: nortelNMIconfigNotiVarbinds
nortelNMIconfigNotiVarbinds.description: This OID represents the branch which contains varbinds to configuration management related notifications.

nortelNMInotifyNeDeEnrolTime.name: nortelNMInotifyNeDeEnrolTime
nortelNMInotifyNeDeEnrolTime.description: This variable represents the time at which the NE for formally deenrolled. NortelNMItimeStampDef textual convention is defined at the NORTEL-NMI-TC-MIB.

nortelNMInotifyNeEnrolTime.name: nortelNMInotifyNeEnrolTime
nortelNMInotifyNeEnrolTime.description: This variable represents the time at which the NE was formally enrolled in the EMS management domain. NortelNMItimeStampDef textual convention is defined at the NORTEL-NMI-TC-MIB.

nortelNMInotifyNeIPaddress.name: nortelNMInotifyNeIPaddress
nortelNMInotifyNeIPaddress.description: This variable represents the IP address of the Network Element, with which an NMS can reach through to the Network element directly.

nortelNMInotifyNeVersionInfo.name: nortelNMInotifyNeVersionInfo
nortelNMInotifyNeVersionInfo.description: This variable contains the version information of Network Element. Software / Hardware version data can be filled in as values as appropriate to the NE in context.

nortelNMInotifyNeVendorName.name: nortelNMInotifyNeVendorName
nortelNMInotifyNeVendorName.description: This variable contains the Network Element vendor name.

nortelNMInotifyNeLocationName.name: nortelNMInotifyNeLocationName
nortelNMInotifyNeLocationName.description: This variable represents the location information of Network Element. An example could be the Common Language Location Identifier (CLLI) of the NE.

nortelNMInotifyNeDataChangeTime.name: nortelNMInotifyNeDataChangeTime
nortelNMInotifyNeDataChangeTime.description: This variable represents the time at which a certain NE attribute was modified.

nortelNMIneEnrolNotification.name: nortelNMIneEnrolNotification
nortelNMIneEnrolNotification.description: This notification indicates that an NE has been enrolled into the EMS management domain. The varbinds include all the key attributes required by the NMS.

nortelNMIneDeEnrolNotification.name: nortelNMIneDeEnrolNotification
nortelNMIneDeEnrolNotification.description: This notification indicates that an NE has been deenrolled from the EMS management domain.

nortelNMIneAttributeChangeNotification.name: nortelNMIneAttributeChangeNotification
nortelNMIneAttributeChangeNotification.description: This notification indicates that an NE attribute has been changed. The modified value of the specific attribute would be included as the varbind in the actual Notification PDU. We currently support changes to version information, vendor name and location name and the NE Reach through IP address.

nortelNMIneRegistrationNotificationGroup.name: nortelNMIneRegistrationNotificationGroup
nortelNMIneRegistrationNotificationGroup.description: Nortel NMI NE registration notifications group.

nortelNMIneAttrChangeNotificationGroup.name: nortelNMIneAttrChangeNotificationGroup
nortelNMIneAttrChangeNotificationGroup.description: Nortel NMI NE attribute change notification group.
